 ***Key Features***

 Offline & Low-Network Access  
Works seamlessly in **no network** or **low network** areas through:
- Offline chatbot mode  
- WhatsApp-based fallback  

 Digital Health ID  
Every user receives a unique digital health identity for:
- Secure access  
- Validated medical records  
- Seamless appointments  

 Verified Doctors & Practitioners  
All medical practitioners are **verified** before approval to ensure trustworthy healthcare.

***Smart AI Chatbot***  
Helps users:
- Identify symptoms  
- Get first-level guidance  
- Navigate health services  

 Appointment Booking & Reminders  
Book doctor consultations and get **smart reminders** â€” even offline.

